    This class is one of the OpenSIMPPLLE's aquatic types, these are a type of SimpplleType. It was developed as a prototype and is not currently supported.

    Aquatic classes were based on Rosgen types assigned to the stream unit. Choices for these are: A1, A2, A3, A4, B2, B3, B4, C4, D4, E4, G3, G4.

    The other aquatic types are: AQUATIC_ATTRIBUTE, AQUATIC_PROCESS, AQUATIC_TREATMENT, LTA_VS_GROUP
